Package org.apache.activemq.artemis.core.deployers

Interface Deployable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileConfiguration, FileJMSConfiguration, LegacyJMSConfiguration
    public interface Deployable
    A Deployable is an object that can be configured via an xml configuration element in the main configuration file "broker.xml" It holds all the information needed by the FileDeploymentManager to parse the configuration and build the component
